<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Node.js - MongoDB CRUD APP</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Wellcome to our Node.js - MongoDB CRUD APP</h1>
    <div>
        <h2>Insert new quote</h2>
        <form action="/quotes" method="post">
            Name: <input type="text" name="name">
            Quote: <input type="text" name="quote">
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <h1>הציטוטים הנבחרים</h1>
    <div>
        <ul>
            <% for(var i=0; i <quotes.length; i++){ %>
                <li>
                    <span>
                        <b>
                            <%= quotes[i].name %>
                        </b>
                    </span>:
                    <span>
                        <i>
                            <%= quotes[i].quote %>
                        </i>
                    </span>
                </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div>
        <h2>Update Some quote</h2>
        <p>החלף את שם הכותב שנקרא הרצל בכותב שיקרא אחאב</p>
        <button id="updateBtn">Update</button>
    </div>
    <hr>
    <div>
        <h2>מחק את אחאב</h2>
        <button id="deleteBtn">Delete</button>
    </div>
    <script src="./main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>